title: Don't Need Nothin' But A Good Zeit 2/1: Wordle, NFL, Spotify, 'Euphoria', Harry Styles, Winter Storm, Ben Simmons
itunes:title: Don't Need Nothin' But A Good Zeit 2/1: Wordle, NFL, Spotify, 'Euphoria', Harry Styles, Winter Storm, Ben Simmons
description:
In this edition of Don't Need Nothin' But A Good Zeit, Jack and super producer Becca discuss the NYT buying Wordle, Tom Brady retiring from the NFL, the Super Bowl, the Joe Rogan/Spotify saga, 'Euphoria' being all over the shop, Harry Styles' birthday, the incipient winter storms about to sweep the US, and the continuing Ben Simmons saga
